name: CW: Star Wars
tagline: A roleplaying universe taking place a long time ago in a galaxy far, far away.
body:
### Introduction
Your server will need to download all of the necessary addons if you don't want to see error models everywhere.

http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/Workshop_for_Dedicated_Servers

The gamemode's workshop collection ID is **693723945**

Please remember this is the first preliminary version of the gamemode. It isn't finished yet.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
